OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and cloudy on Friday, perhaps the
OL,7,Fodd light shower at first. Rain
OL,8,Fspreading southeast on Saturday, drier
OL,9,Fwith a few showers later. Mainly dry
OL,10,Fon Sunday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
